# Mock Data Architecture

All data is mocked. No real Marriott API connections. Every field is annotated
with the real production source it would come from.

## Seed File Index
| File | Contents | Production Source |
|---|---|---|
| `data/seeds/hotels.json` | 8–10 Marriott properties with eco data | Opera PMS + MESH |
| `data/seeds/partners_nyc.json` | 20+ local partners near NYC Marriott | Google Places + partner agreements |
| `data/seeds/partners_dc.json` | 20+ local partners near DC Marriott | Same |
| `data/seeds/partners_chicago.json` | 20+ local partners near Chicago Marriott | Same |
| `data/seeds/guests.json` | 3 personas: Alex, Jordan, Sam | Bonvoy UGI system |
| `data/seeds/stays.json` | Pre-loaded upcoming stays per persona | MARSHA/ACRS reservations |
| `data/seeds/events.json` | 5 events per demo city | Ticketmaster API |
| `data/seeds/restaurants.json` | 10 restaurants per city with dietary tags | Opera PMS F&B + partner DB |
| `data/seeds/arrival_brief_alex.json` | Pre-built brief fixture for Alex | Generated once, saved |
| `data/seeds/arrival_brief_jordan.json` | Pre-built brief fixture for Jordan | Generated once, saved |
| `data/seeds/arrival_brief_sam.json` | Pre-built brief fixture for Sam | Generated once, saved |

